\(L^1\) regularization

library(glmnet)
x <- model.matrix(Fertility ~ ., swiss)[, -1]
y <- swiss$Fertility
fit <- glmnet(x, y)
plot(fit, xvar = "lambda")

cvfit <- cv.glmnet(x, y)
plot(cvfit)

coef(cvfit, s = "lambda.1se")
